title: Watch: NCT 127’s Jaehyun Is Sleek And Smooth In New “Limitless” Teasers
text:
As NCT 127 approaches their comeback date, the group has released new teasers for member Jaehyun! 
The teasers are filled with bright and bold colors, and show Jaehyun sporting blonde hair as he showcases more of NCT 127’s choreography for “Limitless.” NCT 127 is holding a V Live broadcast on January 3, and is set to hold their comeback performance on Mnet’s “M!Countdown” on January 5. Check out the teasers for Jaehyun below!
